    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life, offering a dependable driving experience for the next owner. The exterior still shines beautifully, though a close inspection will reveal some minor road chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smooth and has a documented service history, making it a solid, worry-free choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car.",
